commentText: JSCH is verbose logging out of the box. Therefore we turn the logging down to DEBUG logging by default._But setting this option to <tt>true</tt> turns on the verbose logging again.
codeText: public void setVerboseLogging(boolean verboseLogging) {_        this.verboseLogging = verboseLogging__    }
